  <brief_title>Study Evaluating the Efficacy of Allogeneic Transplant Conditioning With Adaptive Dose Busulfan Intravenous (Busilvex®) in Patients at High Risk of Carrying Blood Diseases</brief_title>
  <acronym>BX-PK</acronym>
